headline: Patients in the US undergo first doses of GE HealthCare’s new PET radiotracer, Flyrcado (flurpiridaz F 18) injection
summary: ARLINGTON HEIGHTS, Ill., February 25, 2025--Patients undergo first doses of GE HealthCare's PET radiotracer Flyrcado (flurpiridaz F 18) injection at early adopter sites in the US.
